e Butler Florida d as second class mail mat ter April 8 1921 at the Post e at Lake Butler Flor da under the At of March 3 1879 SUBSCRIPTION RATE 200 per yearln Advance z member 125 six monthsin advance FLORIDA PRFGC Advertising Rates Cheerfully furnished at this office ASSOCI ATION NATIONAL EDITORIAL I lIASSOCIATION We Commend Governor Warren Recommend Governor Fuller Warren for his offered personal Lnancial sacrifices towards economy for the tax payers of Florida He recently indicated his willingness and desire to forego im mediate pay ment of three months salary in order that the execut le department budget may be balanced We hope that cabinet members and all state employees may come forth now and join the Governor in his determined reduct ion of spending The income and the business of the average indvidual is rapidly declining and in fact many believe that we arc already heading into a most serious financial depression The puces of many common commodities are nosing downward and in tact have fallen rapidly in the last 12 months During the next three years many anticipate that prices"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-01-27T17:02:43.382Z", "group": ["ndnp/fu", "university-of-florida-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn95047168/1949-06-24/ed-1/?sp=2", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_madison_ver01:data:sn95047168:00541310514:1949062401:0196/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=508&w=364", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:fu:batch_fu_madison_ver01:data:sn95047168:00541310514:1949062401:0196/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1017&w=729", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/fu/batch_fu_madison_ver01/data/sn95047168/00541310514/1949062401/0196.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["union county", "florida", "united states", "union", "lake butler"], "location_city": ["lake butler"], "